It took till midnight, so everybody went to bed, which is God's way of telling you, you should go to bed before midnight.

18:33.796 --> 18:34.016
No.

18:37.823 --> 18:42.391
What made the person wise or foolish was not that they both did a very normal thing.

18:43.133 --> 18:44.696
