18:46.118 --> 18:50.546
So to be wise and yet waiting means you need to work.

18:50.818 --> 19:04.511
You need to care for your family and your friends and if you're a student to get educated and if you're working to work hard and if you're getting old to plan for retirement and if you need a nap to rest because rest is worship too.

19:08.175 --> 19:12.279
Nothing was different except one group had oil.

